title: Mathematical Problems
creator: David Hilbert
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Mathematical Problems by David Hilbert. Read by Prachi Pendse Lecture delivered before the International Congress of Mathematicians at Paris in 1900 and subsequently published in the Bulletin of the American Mathematical Society Vol. 8 (1902), 479-481. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
